<h3 class="govuk-heading-m" id="Let users select a single file">Let users see the status of their upload</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">Use a yellow 'UPLOADING' <a class="govuk-link" href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/components/tag/">tag</a> to show the user that their file is being uploaded or scanned.</p>

