<p class="govuk-body">Use a green 'UPLOADED' <a class="govuk-link" href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/components/tag/">tag</a> to show the user that their file has been uploaded and scanned successfully. Link to a copy of the file from the filename.</p>

{{
  example({
